WEBVTT

01:50.200 --> 01:53.970
[Love Between Lines]

01:54.280 --> 01:56.820
[Episode 4]

02:13.470 --> 02:13.840
Xiu.

02:13.840 --> 02:15.710
There's a customer coming to pick up
their pre-ordered coffee beans.

02:15.710 --> 02:17.120
Help me go to the shop first
and open the door.

02:17.120 --> 02:19.630
Ms. Zhao, you're ordering me around
already?

02:19.630 --> 02:20.560
Of course.

02:20.560 --> 02:22.750
How can I waste free labor?

02:23.520 --> 02:24.780
Alright, I'm on my way.

02:24.960 --> 02:25.190
By the way,

02:25.190 --> 02:26.840
remember to take a photo of
your ID and send it to me.

02:26.840 --> 02:28.870
I'll give it to the park's
property management for registration.

02:28.870 --> 02:30.470
That way, you'll be able to enter
and leave freely

02:30.470 --> 02:31.680
even outside business hours.

02:31.680 --> 02:34.079
Alright, just a minute.
I'll send it to you.

02:48.480 --> 02:49.570
A bumper pad?

03:01.130 --> 03:03.080
Mr. Gong, are you in?

03:04.300 --> 03:05.430
It's still so early.

03:05.710 --> 03:07.170
He's already gone to work?

03:10.800 --> 03:11.360
Mr. Gong.

03:11.360 --> 03:12.520
Sorry to bother you.

03:12.520 --> 03:14.560
When I came to
sign the contract yesterday,

03:14.560 --> 03:16.150
I think I accidentally left my cardholder

03:16.150 --> 03:17.280
on the sofa.

03:17.430 --> 03:18.590
When would be a good time for me

03:18.590 --> 03:19.920
to come by and pick it up?

03:29.350 --> 03:32.230
[Gong Huaicong]

03:31.710 --> 03:32.630
Mr. Gong?

03:35.380 --> 03:36.950
You're in, right, Mr. Gong?

03:42.840 --> 03:43.370
Thank...

03:45.000 --> 03:45.840
Thank you.

03:46.490 --> 03:47.770
Are you okay?

03:48.740 --> 03:50.140
I've got some allergies—

03:50.290 --> 03:52.220
can't really see people right now.

03:53.120 --> 03:55.980
He just moved in
and he's already having allergies?

04:04.630 --> 04:05.540
Mr. Gong.

04:05.770 --> 04:07.470
I thought it might not be convenient
for you to go out,

04:07.470 --> 04:08.710
so I bought you some allergy medicine.

04:08.710 --> 04:10.440
I'll leave it at your doorstep.

04:28.430 --> 04:29.720
So polite?

04:31.610 --> 04:32.320
Zhao.

04:32.600 --> 04:33.120
Xiu.

04:33.120 --> 04:34.000
Come help me.

04:34.000 --> 04:35.600
I can't handle it by myself anymore.

04:35.600 --> 04:36.120
Okay.

04:36.360 --> 04:37.020
Checkmate.

04:40.190 --> 04:41.310
No. 27.

04:42.560 --> 04:43.390
Thank you.

04:44.159 --> 04:45.950
Why are there so many customers today?

04:45.950 --> 04:47.560
All thanks to the shop across the street.

04:47.560 --> 04:49.480
They're all here for
the murder mystery game?

04:49.480 --> 04:50.070
I asked,

04:50.070 --> 04:52.120
and they said another post about it
went viral on the internet.

04:52.120 --> 04:53.310
The data was really good.

04:53.310 --> 04:53.680
Look.

04:53.680 --> 04:55.560
Since it's Friday night, many people
have come over to catch the late sessions.

04:55.560 --> 04:57.600
They're all taking photos outside
and waiting to get in.

04:57.600 --> 05:00.260
How many more cups?
I'll go deliver them for you.

05:11.330 --> 05:12.650
So he's rich.

05:16.830 --> 05:17.600
Wait.

05:18.200 --> 05:22.400
He has allergies, yet he still came so far
just to play a murder mystery game?

05:27.210 --> 05:29.100
His license plate is also local.

05:32.510 --> 05:33.840
Who ordered the coffee?

05:34.480 --> 05:34.920
It's ours.

05:34.920 --> 05:35.600
Here.

05:35.600 --> 05:36.200
Thank you.

05:36.560 --> 05:37.680
There're name tags on the cups.

05:37.680 --> 05:38.680
Don't mix them up.

05:41.580 --> 05:42.909
Hello, long time no see.

05:42.950 --> 05:44.510
But there are
quite a lot of people here today.

05:44.510 --> 05:45.720
We might not be able to get you in.

05:45.720 --> 05:48.650
I noticed a player came in as soon as
he parked his car.

05:48.950 --> 05:50.040
That's our boss.

05:50.040 --> 05:51.900
All the players are waiting here.

05:52.950 --> 05:53.830
That red car

05:53.830 --> 05:55.190
belongs to your boss?

05:55.560 --> 05:57.180
Mr. Gong's got a new car again?

05:57.180 --> 05:58.100
Yeah.

05:58.310 --> 06:00.000
He looks really happy today.

06:00.630 --> 06:01.390
You have no idea.

06:01.390 --> 06:02.610
Once he changes his car,

06:02.610 --> 06:04.680
it means he's got a new girlfriend.

06:22.680 --> 06:24.510
So everything he said about coming here

06:24.510 --> 06:26.040
on a business trip was a lie.

06:26.520 --> 06:28.850
Then what's his point in renting my place?

06:34.390 --> 06:35.870
Gong Huaicong...

06:36.630 --> 06:38.680
Qin Xiaoyi...

06:46.560 --> 06:47.830
He's not home.

06:47.830 --> 06:48.760
That matches up.

06:51.240 --> 06:53.070
I-I must be overthinking it.

06:56.870 --> 06:57.510
Why-

07:17.600 --> 07:18.270
Don't talk.

07:18.440 --> 07:19.590
I'm not talking.

07:38.630 --> 07:39.430
Ms. Hu,

07:39.860 --> 07:41.690
a fox can't be the winner here.

07:49.720 --> 07:51.070
I can't just let it go.

07:56.270 --> 07:57.920
Have Dong Qi report directly to me.

07:57.920 --> 07:59.310
We'll discuss the rest when you get back.

07:59.310 --> 08:00.120
That works.

08:00.310 --> 08:01.240
Just park here.

08:01.600 --> 08:02.120
Here.

08:02.630 --> 08:03.360
Why is it so noisy over there?

08:03.360 --> 08:04.960
Just deliver it to this door.

08:05.040 --> 08:06.190
No. 27.

08:06.190 --> 08:07.190
-It's the first door.
-Okay.

08:07.190 --> 08:08.750
And then deliver it to the second floor.

08:08.750 --> 08:09.920
Okay, okay. It's alright.

08:09.920 --> 08:10.480
Be careful.

08:10.480 --> 08:11.510
The doorway is a bit narrow.

08:11.510 --> 08:13.120
Maybe just tilt it and slide it in.

08:13.120 --> 08:14.310
The stairs aren't easy to climb, either.

08:14.310 --> 08:15.770
Thanks for your hard work.

08:19.830 --> 08:21.070
Watch out behind you.

08:21.750 --> 08:22.240
Alright, alright.

08:22.240 --> 08:23.680
Be careful not to damage it.

08:23.680 --> 08:24.680
Alright, alright.

08:24.680 --> 08:26.210
Be careful not to damage it.

08:34.030 --> 08:34.960
Mr. Gong.

08:36.000 --> 08:37.270
You're home, right?

08:37.909 --> 08:38.840
It just occurred to me

08:38.840 --> 08:40.320
that the bed in the attic is quite old,

08:40.320 --> 08:42.580
so I bought a new one
and had it delivered.

08:43.919 --> 08:44.990
What happened?

08:45.150 --> 08:46.150
Are you okay?

08:49.870 --> 08:50.670
Mr. Gong.

08:51.290 --> 08:53.290
I was worried the bed might collapse

08:53.390 --> 08:55.390
when you sleep at night,

08:55.390 --> 08:56.870
so I rushed over here on purpose.

08:56.870 --> 08:58.390
I know you're in there.

08:58.390 --> 09:00.650
Is there anything inconvenient for you?

09:02.030 --> 09:03.620
Just leave the bed at the door.

09:03.620 --> 09:04.720
I'll carry it in myself.

09:04.720 --> 09:05.440
That won't work.

09:05.440 --> 09:07.960
The delivery guys
need to install it inside,

09:07.960 --> 09:10.150
take photos, and confirm
with the store before they leave.

09:10.150 --> 09:10.950
That's right.

09:11.120 --> 09:12.520
It's our company policy.

09:18.590 --> 09:20.420
Xiao, do you have time
to come by the club sometime soon?

09:20.420 --> 09:22.430
Just hurry over. She's blocking my door.

09:22.430 --> 09:23.910
Mr. Gong.

09:24.390 --> 09:25.310
Mr. Gong?

09:32.110 --> 09:33.030
Ms. Hu.

09:33.030 --> 09:34.510
I still need to tidy up a bit.

09:34.510 --> 09:36.680
Would you mind going to
the property management office?

09:36.680 --> 09:38.790
There was a payment reminder
posted on the door yesterday.

09:38.790 --> 09:40.450
I don't know what fee it's for.

09:40.670 --> 09:42.550
Alright, I'll go check it first

09:42.550 --> 09:43.790
and come by later.

09:44.080 --> 09:44.720
Well, since

09:44.720 --> 09:45.440
this hallway is narrow,

09:45.440 --> 09:46.910
how about we leave it here for now?

09:46.910 --> 09:47.960
I'll take you guys downstairs to wait,

09:47.960 --> 09:49.480
and we can grab some water on the way.

09:49.480 --> 09:51.240
After the tenant finishes tidying up,

09:51.240 --> 09:52.510
we'll come back up.

09:53.030 --> 09:53.790
Alright then.

09:53.790 --> 09:54.670
Thank you.

10:23.630 --> 10:24.390
Mr. Gong.

10:24.630 --> 10:26.000
I just checked with property management,

10:26.000 --> 10:27.200
and they said
there's no outstanding payment.

10:27.200 --> 10:28.630
Could there be a mistake?

10:28.840 --> 10:30.500
Have you finished tidying up?

10:30.870 --> 10:33.390
Didn't you say you had arrived?
Where are you?

10:33.390 --> 10:34.030
I

10:34.720 --> 10:35.870
got the wrong door.

10:36.240 --> 10:37.480
I'm next door to you.

10:40.370 --> 10:41.480
Mr. Gong.

10:42.660 --> 10:43.450
Mr. Gong.

10:46.360 --> 10:48.490
Are your balconies next to each other?

10:49.080 --> 10:50.080
I think so.

10:50.510 --> 10:51.480
You're not thinking of...

10:51.480 --> 10:53.210
I'm going all out for you today.

10:57.000 --> 10:58.660
You almost scared me to death!

11:06.750 --> 11:07.600
Go put on these pajamas.

11:07.600 --> 11:08.670
Let's make this act convincing.

11:08.670 --> 11:09.670
I'll go hide in the attic wardrobe.

11:09.670 --> 11:10.550
Don't blow our cover.

11:10.550 --> 11:10.790
But

11:10.790 --> 11:12.750
this isn't even my usual dressing style.

11:12.750 --> 11:13.910
Mr. Gong!

11:17.790 --> 11:18.600
I'm sorry, Ms. Hu,

11:18.600 --> 11:20.000
for keeping you waiting.

11:21.360 --> 11:22.440
That's very thoughtful of you,

11:22.440 --> 11:24.240
bringing a new bed.

11:25.360 --> 11:26.270
Well, it's actually a coincidence.

11:26.270 --> 11:29.120
Since I was thinking about
renting out this place a while ago,

11:29.120 --> 11:30.550
I bought a new wardrobe.

11:31.150 --> 11:32.510
W-Wardrobe?

11:33.000 --> 11:34.390
W-What wardrobe?

11:34.390 --> 11:35.670
The one in the attic.

11:36.270 --> 11:38.240
It's the same brand as this bed.

11:38.240 --> 11:38.960
And then I thought,

11:38.960 --> 11:40.480
since they gave me a discount coupon,

11:40.480 --> 11:41.320
I might as well use it.

11:41.320 --> 11:43.270
So I went ahead and bought this bed too.

11:43.270 --> 11:43.840
I see.

11:43.840 --> 11:45.150
Thank you then.

11:47.600 --> 11:48.150
No need to change your shoes.

11:48.150 --> 11:49.150
Just come right in.

11:49.150 --> 11:51.100
I'll have the delivery guys
come in to install it then.

11:51.100 --> 11:51.650
Okay.

11:51.910 --> 11:52.510
Come on in.

11:55.270 --> 11:56.390
Thank you for your hard work.

11:56.390 --> 11:57.190
It's nothing.

12:10.790 --> 12:12.270
I need to use the restroom.

12:12.800 --> 12:13.800
Please, go ahead.

12:22.080 --> 12:23.440
The new bed is installed.

12:23.440 --> 12:25.080
We'll take the old one downstairs.

12:25.080 --> 12:26.030
Thank you for your trouble.

12:26.030 --> 12:27.630
It's okay, no trouble at all.

12:30.910 --> 12:31.670
Mr. Gong.

12:32.000 --> 12:34.440
This bed replacement
was actually due to my oversight.

12:34.440 --> 12:36.320
These old pieces of furniture
are prone to problems.

12:36.320 --> 12:37.080
Now that

12:37.080 --> 12:37.870
I'm here,

12:37.870 --> 12:38.670
I might as well help you

12:38.670 --> 12:40.080
check the rest of them too,

12:40.080 --> 12:41.880
especially the one in the attic.

12:43.100 --> 12:44.100
It's okay, Ms. Hu.

12:44.120 --> 12:45.520
No need for such trouble.

12:48.840 --> 12:50.790
There's actually nothing
that needs checking.

12:50.790 --> 12:52.030
Apart from the bed,

12:52.480 --> 12:54.880
the other pieces of furniture
are all fine.

12:56.000 --> 12:56.720
It's okay.

12:56.720 --> 13:00.320
Let's have everything checked,
so we can both have peace of mind.

13:01.670 --> 13:03.200
Especially this wardrobe.

13:17.970 --> 13:18.540
Mom.

13:18.750 --> 13:20.750
Why didn't you reply to my messages?

13:20.910 --> 13:22.370
It's finally the weekend.

13:22.440 --> 13:23.480
Come back for dinner.

13:23.480 --> 13:24.390
Okay, got it.

13:24.390 --> 13:25.440
I'll be home soon.

13:29.480 --> 13:32.560
Let's skip the wardrobe.
It's a bit inconvenient.

13:34.930 --> 13:36.580
Personal stuff?

13:36.600 --> 13:37.170
Yeah.

13:39.150 --> 13:39.880
Understood.

13:40.870 --> 13:41.910
I'll be going then.

13:41.910 --> 13:42.910
I'll walk you out.

13:49.300 --> 13:49.990
Bye-bye.

13:53.870 --> 13:54.750
Dazhong.

13:55.790 --> 13:56.430
Going out?

13:58.250 --> 13:59.170
Bad cat.

14:02.390 --> 14:03.850
She didn't close the door.

14:08.240 --> 14:09.840
She's definitely thinking

14:09.840 --> 14:11.910
there's something scandalous
in that wardrobe.

14:11.910 --> 14:13.320
Seriously,

14:14.270 --> 14:16.470
I already told her I'd handle it myself.

14:16.750 --> 14:18.080
Do you think she's being well-meaning,

14:18.080 --> 14:19.410
or she's just too naive?

14:19.980 --> 14:20.550
You know what?

14:20.550 --> 14:22.270
Good thing I showed up in time today.

14:22.270 --> 14:23.510
Otherwise, you'd be finished,

14:23.510 --> 14:24.440
I'd be finished too,

14:24.440 --> 14:26.960
and my hard-earned reputation
would be ruined in one stroke.

14:26.960 --> 14:28.840
She might even kick you out.

14:31.320 --> 14:32.270
What's going on?

14:33.200 --> 14:34.860
Still not back to your senses?

14:36.720 --> 14:37.870
We've been exposed.

14:38.900 --> 14:40.410
No way.

14:41.050 --> 14:43.440
Everything was fine
when I saw her off just now.

14:43.440 --> 14:44.240
If we had really been exposed,

14:44.240 --> 14:45.870
she wouldn't have stayed silent.

14:45.870 --> 14:47.840
Didn't she tell you
that wardrobe was newly purchased?

14:47.840 --> 14:49.770
Yes, it's the same brand as the bed.

14:49.910 --> 14:51.810
And didn't she say
she wanted to check the old furniture?

14:51.810 --> 14:53.740
Why did she check the new piece too?

14:56.750 --> 14:57.910
So you mean she...

14:58.390 --> 14:59.390
Knew all along?

15:00.080 --> 15:02.010
Then why didn't she just expose us?

15:03.630 --> 15:04.790
I don't care what she thinks.

15:04.790 --> 15:06.240
If this happens again,

15:06.390 --> 15:08.030
I suggest you come clean.

15:08.960 --> 15:11.200
No need to thank me
for helping you this time.

15:11.200 --> 15:12.630
Just do one more show for me.

15:12.630 --> 15:13.270
I'm leaving.

15:13.270 --> 15:14.330
Let me walk you out,

15:14.840 --> 15:17.240
so you don't end up
at the neighbor's again.

15:36.600 --> 15:38.080
Xiu, you're back.

15:40.510 --> 15:42.000
Dinner will be ready soon.

15:43.030 --> 15:44.720
Is there anything I can help with?

15:44.720 --> 15:45.550
No need.

15:45.960 --> 15:47.080
You just got off work. You must be tired.

15:47.080 --> 15:48.030
Go rest.

15:48.670 --> 15:49.550
That's right.

15:51.510 --> 15:52.150
Xiu.

15:52.750 --> 15:54.360
You've been back
at the company for a while now.

15:54.360 --> 15:55.480
How has it been?

15:55.720 --> 15:56.840
After taking such a long leave,

15:56.840 --> 15:58.430
has Mr. Xu given you any trouble?

15:58.430 --> 16:00.150
It would be normal

16:00.170 --> 16:01.630
if Mr. Xu gave her trouble.

16:01.720 --> 16:03.080
What do you mean normal?

16:03.430 --> 16:04.860
Our Xiu is so capable.

16:04.880 --> 16:06.610
She never took a day off before.

16:06.750 --> 16:08.950
What's wrong with taking a short break?

16:09.770 --> 16:11.370
If you really think so,

16:11.400 --> 16:13.400
then why did you prepare that thing?

16:14.910 --> 16:16.220
What do you mean?

16:19.840 --> 16:21.440
I've prepared a gift for you

16:21.750 --> 16:23.840
to give to Mr. Xu on Monday.

16:24.510 --> 16:25.550
What gift?

16:27.150 --> 16:28.410
Two bottles of Moutai—

16:28.510 --> 16:30.240
your dad's prized collection.

16:30.240 --> 16:31.390
Remember to take them with you later.

16:31.390 --> 16:32.750
Such expensive gifts

16:32.750 --> 16:34.550
would be wasted on Mr. Xu.

16:36.320 --> 16:37.720
As a GM assistant,

16:37.870 --> 16:39.840
it's important to maintain
a good relationship with your boss

16:39.840 --> 16:41.750
and show a positive attitude, you know?

16:41.750 --> 16:42.600
Be a good girl.

16:44.830 --> 16:46.310
I'll put them away first.

16:46.870 --> 16:48.560
I-I'll find a bag to pack them.

16:48.580 --> 16:49.180
Okay.

16:56.870 --> 16:57.630
To part with that wine

16:57.630 --> 16:59.000
makes my heart ache.

17:05.880 --> 17:06.440
Dad.

17:06.880 --> 17:07.410
Alright.

17:11.480 --> 17:11.920
Dinner's ready.

17:11.920 --> 17:13.579
Hello, this is Zhuling Group.

17:13.680 --> 17:15.069
We've reviewed your resume

17:15.069 --> 17:16.480
and would like to know if you could come

17:16.480 --> 17:18.339
for an interview on Monday at 1 PM.

17:23.869 --> 17:26.400
Where did you say
you were calling from again?

17:27.260 --> 17:28.830
Zhuling Group.

17:32.790 --> 17:34.650
I'll definitely be there on time.

17:42.440 --> 17:43.240
What's wrong?

17:44.070 --> 17:45.310
Who was that?

17:45.510 --> 17:47.110
What's with all the secrecy?

17:50.160 --> 17:51.880
If there's anything new going on,

17:51.880 --> 17:53.590
remember to let us know.

17:53.960 --> 17:54.960
When dating someone,

17:54.960 --> 17:56.720
you need to keep your eyes wide open.

17:56.720 --> 17:58.480
But it was just a spam call.

17:59.570 --> 18:01.000
Let's eat. I'm starving.

18:05.550 --> 18:06.350
So delicious.

19:09.880 --> 19:10.550
Mr. Gong,

19:10.550 --> 19:11.960
I sent you a message yesterday.

19:11.960 --> 19:13.590
I need to go home to grab something today.

19:13.590 --> 19:15.070
What time will you be there?

19:15.070 --> 19:16.130
Here you are, Miss.

19:16.150 --> 19:17.020
Thank you, Sir.

19:20.090 --> 19:21.170
You can come over now.

19:21.170 --> 19:21.700
I'm home.

19:22.160 --> 19:23.000
He's home?

19:23.270 --> 19:25.640
Aren't those two tired of

19:25.910 --> 19:28.110
putting on a show like that all the time?

19:32.430 --> 19:34.290
Are you sure this is the last time?

19:34.590 --> 19:35.480
I am sure.

19:35.640 --> 19:37.640
I'll come clean with her in a moment.

19:38.310 --> 19:39.920
Why the sudden change of heart?

19:39.920 --> 19:41.270
Maybe because

19:41.270 --> 19:42.920
lies mess with the fengshui,

19:43.420 --> 19:45.260
and the fengshui messes with my sleep.

19:45.260 --> 19:46.790
What nonsense.

19:47.580 --> 19:49.380
Remember to sign a new contract,

19:49.470 --> 19:51.510
so your drama doesn't affect me.

19:52.270 --> 19:54.200
You don't have to worry about that.

19:56.240 --> 19:56.840
By the way,

19:57.440 --> 19:59.680
what did you say
she was coming to get again?

19:59.680 --> 20:00.730
Something big or small?

20:00.730 --> 20:02.330
S-Something small, I think.

20:02.970 --> 20:05.580
There's a box on top of the fridge
in the living room.

20:05.580 --> 20:07.640
She said something about documents.

20:08.070 --> 20:09.270
You're not planning to

20:09.270 --> 20:10.830
get it ready for her in advance, are you?

20:10.830 --> 20:11.270
Let me tell you,

20:11.270 --> 20:13.800
flattery isn't supposed to be
done like that.

20:13.920 --> 20:16.160
I just want to get this over with quickly.

20:16.160 --> 20:17.440
Take your time getting it over then.

20:17.440 --> 20:19.300
Just don't get yourself trapped.

20:22.590 --> 20:23.920
Why aren't you talking?

20:24.670 --> 20:27.160
What did Hu Xiu do for work before,

20:27.350 --> 20:28.610
and where did she work?

20:28.830 --> 20:30.000
Is she an architect?

20:30.270 --> 20:31.200
I don't think so.

20:31.500 --> 20:34.300
She doesn't look like
someone in your profession.

20:35.000 --> 20:35.860
I remember now.

20:35.920 --> 20:36.680
She mentioned before

20:36.680 --> 20:40.280
that she used to work as an assistant
at some real estate company.

20:40.320 --> 20:41.720
Later, she quit that job,

20:41.820 --> 20:43.280
and now she's unemployed,

20:43.820 --> 20:45.830
living off the rent she collects from us.

20:45.830 --> 20:46.630
What's wrong?

20:47.040 --> 20:47.650
Nothing.

20:47.680 --> 20:49.080
I might be overthinking.

20:49.110 --> 20:49.770
Hanging up.

20:52.590 --> 20:54.200
[Galaxy Bookstore & Library]

20:58.790 --> 21:01.040
Ms. Hu, I had to go out
for something urgent.

21:01.040 --> 21:03.280
The key is under the doormat.

21:03.410 --> 21:05.010
Just let yourself in.

21:06.720 --> 21:08.780
How nice of him to bring it down for me.

21:21.580 --> 21:26.790
♪ Close your eyes for me ♪

21:27.810 --> 21:29.810
♪ Don't rush to wake up ♪

21:30.030 --> 21:33.770
♪ Let the night pass more slowly ♪

21:36.330 --> 21:40.770
♪ Will you stay with me? ♪

21:42.540 --> 21:44.540
♪ Don't ask for why ♪

21:45.190 --> 21:48.490
♪ No need for words, let it be ♪

21:50.370 --> 21:52.200
♪ You won't know ♪

21:52.230 --> 21:55.600
♪ I so often feel alone ♪

21:57.720 --> 22:00.120
♪ But watching you ♪

22:00.230 --> 22:04.430
♪ How come I feel solaced ♪

22:05.480 --> 22:07.920
Xiu is currently staying
on the second floor of our café.

22:07.920 --> 22:09.030
Just FYI.

22:09.350 --> 22:10.310
Pretend that you don't know.

22:10.310 --> 22:12.170
I don't want her to feel burdened.

22:15.920 --> 22:17.050
What's on your mind?

22:20.430 --> 22:21.460
I was thinking

22:21.480 --> 22:23.550
it would be nice if our place
were a bit bigger.

22:23.550 --> 22:24.750
That way, it would be more convenient

22:24.750 --> 22:25.670
for our family and friends

22:25.670 --> 22:27.320
to come over and stay.

22:27.880 --> 22:29.270
I don't know about others,

22:29.270 --> 22:30.920
but I know Xiu well.

22:31.110 --> 22:33.070
Even if we had a big mansion,

22:33.300 --> 22:35.920
she wouldn't want to stay here
and be the third wheel.

22:35.920 --> 22:37.000
So you

22:37.000 --> 22:38.330
needn't worry too much.

22:38.960 --> 22:40.690
I quite like this place as it is.

22:43.310 --> 22:44.400
All done.

22:48.880 --> 22:50.000
Look at you.

22:50.110 --> 22:51.550
You've been working overtime
nonstop lately,

22:51.550 --> 22:52.880
coming home so late,

22:53.400 --> 22:55.990
and yet you're still busy
even after you get back.

22:55.990 --> 22:56.620
Not anymore.

22:56.620 --> 22:58.770
I won't bring work home anymore.

23:00.070 --> 23:01.200
Let's go see a movie.

23:01.270 --> 23:03.360
That new horror film is really good.

23:23.200 --> 23:24.110
Do you remember

23:24.110 --> 23:26.310
our first date in college?

23:26.510 --> 23:27.510
I came to your school to see you,

23:27.510 --> 23:29.510
and you took me to see a horror movie.

23:30.400 --> 23:32.030
I don't know if you were being clueless

23:32.030 --> 23:33.920
or actually quite clever.

24:03.880 --> 24:04.590
Many passengers

24:04.590 --> 24:06.440
take a second look at this building
when passing by.

24:06.440 --> 24:08.160
It seems to be
an internet-famous bookstore,

24:08.160 --> 24:09.160
called Galaxy Bookstore.

24:09.160 --> 24:09.960
It's been around for a few years...

24:09.960 --> 24:10.750
Three years.

24:11.880 --> 24:13.510
Young people really do have better memory.

24:13.300 --> 24:17.600
♪ Under the streetlight,
I grow increasingly weary ♪

24:19.390 --> 24:24.230
♪ A few specks of dust
drift by in the wind ♪

24:26.510 --> 24:30.670
♪ The girl who once
basked in the sunlight ♪

24:31.350 --> 24:34.270
♪ Where did she go to play? ♪

24:34.710 --> 24:37.690
♪ I don't understand either ♪

24:35.110 --> 24:35.880
Excuse me.

24:36.720 --> 24:38.270
I just wanted to say that your bookstore

24:38.270 --> 24:39.680
is really beautifully designed.

24:39.680 --> 24:40.310
Thank you.

24:39.920 --> 24:43.750
♪ Flicking through old chat logs ♪

24:40.310 --> 24:41.240
I'll let our manager

24:41.240 --> 24:42.590
pass that on to the designer.

24:42.590 --> 24:45.190
I remember the designer
is quite young as well.

24:45.390 --> 24:47.190
I know him. I also study architecture.

24:46.000 --> 24:50.890
♪ I just realized the replies
were somewhat delayed ♪

24:47.600 --> 24:48.930
[Mom]

24:48.400 --> 24:49.030
Pardon me.

24:49.030 --> 24:49.680
It's okay.

24:50.610 --> 24:51.130
Mom.

24:51.240 --> 24:52.000
Xiu.

24:52.030 --> 24:58.020
♪ At the crossroads of choices,
amidst the bustling crowd ♪

24:52.220 --> 24:53.790
Your dad and I are at the hospital.

24:53.790 --> 24:54.920
According to the doctor,

24:54.920 --> 24:57.000
his condition can't be treated
conservatively.

24:57.000 --> 24:57.960
He needs surgery.

24:57.960 --> 24:59.070
Mom, Mom, calm down.

24:59.070 --> 25:00.310
I'll head to the hospital right now.

24:59.250 --> 25:06.520
♪ Who hasn't paid the price
and still fallen short? ♪

25:06.540 --> 25:11.090
♪ Stand with me tonight,
look at the starlight ♪

25:11.900 --> 25:17.950
♪ Even if the plot is changed dramatically
by fate again ♪

25:14.920 --> 25:16.850
Hello. I'm here for the interview.

25:18.640 --> 25:24.850
♪ I know the dark clouds will still come ♪

25:25.390 --> 25:33.740
♪ But in this world,
there will always be someone ♪

25:31.030 --> 25:32.200
Check this.

25:32.200 --> 25:33.160
And these two data points—

25:33.160 --> 25:34.460
check them again more carefully.

25:34.460 --> 25:37.740
♪ Who looks forward
with the same hope as me ♪

25:41.270 --> 25:42.310
Ms. Hu, right?

25:42.510 --> 25:43.160
We don't have much time,

25:43.160 --> 25:44.440
so let's get straight to the point.

25:44.440 --> 25:45.030
Okay.

25:49.070 --> 25:51.070
I see on your resume

25:51.200 --> 25:52.400
that during your university years,

25:52.400 --> 25:54.640
you participated in
an architectural design competition.

25:54.640 --> 25:55.160
Yes,

25:55.350 --> 25:57.280
and I've brought the model with me.

25:58.290 --> 25:59.290
No need to bother.

26:00.920 --> 26:02.110
What I mean is

26:02.640 --> 26:04.720
there's no need to review your portfolio.

26:04.720 --> 26:06.830
The honors you mentioned in your resume

26:06.830 --> 26:09.200
are sufficient proof
of your professional competence.

26:09.200 --> 26:10.720
After all, not every architecture student

26:10.720 --> 26:13.320
can win awards
during their university years.

26:13.660 --> 26:14.530
Actually,

26:14.720 --> 26:16.270
we collaborate with

26:16.270 --> 26:17.370
many excellent architects.

26:17.370 --> 26:17.830
It's good

26:17.830 --> 26:20.070
that you have professional knowledge
in architecture.

26:20.070 --> 26:21.550
Your ability
to communicate with architects

26:21.550 --> 26:23.480
is also something we value highly.

26:23.620 --> 26:26.250
I don't quite understand what you mean.

26:26.720 --> 26:27.650
To put it simply,

26:27.830 --> 26:28.480
our general manager

26:28.480 --> 26:29.920
is looking to hire an assistant.

26:29.920 --> 26:32.120
I wonder if you'd be interested, Ms. Hu.

26:32.470 --> 26:34.550
But you called me for an interview

26:34.550 --> 26:37.370
for the assistant architect position,
didn't you?

26:37.370 --> 26:38.570
You should know that

26:39.510 --> 26:40.830
your resume

26:40.830 --> 26:43.680
is actually more suitable for
an administrative assistant position.

26:43.680 --> 26:44.480
Our company, Zhuling,

26:44.480 --> 26:46.500
is a very established architectural firm.

26:46.500 --> 26:48.110
Even a GM assistant

26:48.590 --> 26:50.270
needs solid professional expertise

26:50.270 --> 26:51.350
to be up to the job.

26:52.880 --> 26:55.380
I see that you have more than 3 years
of experience as a GM assistant,

26:55.380 --> 26:56.760
which makes you an even better fit
for this position.

26:56.760 --> 26:59.220
But my plan is to change
my career direction.

27:00.200 --> 27:02.480
If your company could give me
an opportunity,

27:02.480 --> 27:04.040
I'm willing to lower
my salary expectations

27:04.040 --> 27:05.890
and work hard to catch up.

27:07.880 --> 27:08.750
Ms. Hu.

27:09.360 --> 27:11.560
If a car wants to reach its destination,

27:11.820 --> 27:13.220
all it needs is some fuel.

27:13.680 --> 27:15.360
But for a person to succeed,

27:15.650 --> 27:17.310
driving force alone won't do.

27:17.310 --> 27:18.880
You've been working for years.

27:18.880 --> 27:20.310
You should know the market better now

27:20.310 --> 27:21.920
than when you just graduated.

27:21.920 --> 27:24.350
The position of GM assistant

27:24.350 --> 27:25.480
offers far better salary and career scope

27:25.480 --> 27:27.440
than an assistant architect.

27:27.510 --> 27:30.420
Why give up the foundation
you've built over these years?

27:30.420 --> 27:31.990
Those branching crossroads

27:31.990 --> 27:33.200
have always been there,

27:33.200 --> 27:35.440
but what lies ahead

27:35.750 --> 27:36.720
is more likely a trap

27:36.720 --> 27:37.920
than an opportunity.

27:38.270 --> 27:40.330
I hope you give this careful thought.

27:54.040 --> 27:55.970
I've made an appointment with him.

27:59.640 --> 28:00.450
-Mr. Pei.
-Mr. Pei.

28:00.450 --> 28:01.610
Please press the first floor for me.

28:01.610 --> 28:02.370
Thank you.

28:09.270 --> 28:10.510
Who is this?

28:10.880 --> 28:11.440
No idea.

28:30.510 --> 28:31.110
Thanks.

28:40.240 --> 28:42.240
Mr. Xie is here. He's in the tea room.

28:47.270 --> 28:48.160
Uncle Xie,

28:48.750 --> 28:49.880
you finally made it.

28:51.830 --> 28:53.240
The GM of Zhuling asked me to come—

28:53.240 --> 28:54.070
how could I not?

28:54.070 --> 28:55.510
You're too kind, Uncle Xie.

28:55.510 --> 28:56.350
I've prepared

28:56.350 --> 28:57.400
your favorite Wuyi Rock Oolong for you.

28:57.400 --> 28:59.130
Please, sit down and have a try.

29:01.510 --> 29:02.440
Tell me,

29:02.720 --> 29:04.640
what can I help you with?

29:05.510 --> 29:07.770
I heard Lyman is launching a new project.

29:08.200 --> 29:08.750
What,

29:09.240 --> 29:10.840
is Zhuling also interested?

29:11.240 --> 29:11.960
Of course.

29:12.160 --> 29:12.920
Zhuling won't miss out on

29:12.920 --> 29:14.480
any of Lyman's projects.

29:15.030 --> 29:16.110
I wonder which other companies

29:16.110 --> 29:18.510
will be participating in the competition.

29:19.930 --> 29:21.160
Are you trying to ask about

29:21.160 --> 29:22.160
Dynamism?

29:24.120 --> 29:25.050
As you expected,

29:25.210 --> 29:27.140
they've also expressed interest.

29:29.480 --> 29:30.610
I didn't expect that

29:31.400 --> 29:33.200
a firm that gained fame through hype

29:33.200 --> 29:34.790
is also joining the competition.

29:34.790 --> 29:36.120
They've got some nerve.

29:36.200 --> 29:36.790
Of course

29:36.790 --> 29:38.310
Dynamism's got some nerve.

29:38.310 --> 29:39.790
Otherwise, how would they have dared

29:39.790 --> 29:41.000
to keep stealing projects

29:41.000 --> 29:42.660
from Zhuling all these years?

29:43.550 --> 29:44.380
Let's not talk about this anymore.

29:44.380 --> 29:45.580
Today is just for tea.

29:46.030 --> 29:46.440
Alright.

29:46.440 --> 29:46.810
Here.

29:55.960 --> 29:56.750
Ms. Hu.

29:57.350 --> 29:59.550
If a car wants to reach its destination,

29:59.830 --> 30:01.230
all it needs is some fuel.

30:01.440 --> 30:03.160
But for a person to succeed,

30:03.440 --> 30:04.920
driving force alone won't do.

30:04.920 --> 30:06.440
Those branching crossroads

30:06.440 --> 30:07.640
have always been there,

30:07.640 --> 30:09.920
but what lies ahead

30:10.130 --> 30:11.070
is more likely a trap

30:11.070 --> 30:12.270
than an opportunity.

30:20.920 --> 30:22.680
Hello, is this Ms. Hu

30:22.680 --> 30:24.640
from No. 27, Lane 9, Yanhua Road?

30:25.090 --> 30:25.950
Yes, speaking.

30:31.880 --> 30:32.510
Stop here!

30:32.620 --> 30:34.420
I've been watching you for days.

30:34.480 --> 30:36.440
You've been wandering around our lane,

30:36.440 --> 30:37.790
looking and taking notes.

30:37.790 --> 30:38.900
What exactly are you up to?

30:38.900 --> 30:40.840
I live here. What's wrong

30:40.860 --> 30:42.460
with me walking around a bit?

30:42.590 --> 30:43.720
I already checked with
property management.

30:43.720 --> 30:44.960
There's no record of you at all

30:44.960 --> 30:47.000
in the tenant information.

30:48.960 --> 30:50.030
Whether I live here or not

30:50.030 --> 30:51.480
is very easy to prove.

30:54.160 --> 30:54.960
What's wrong?

30:55.420 --> 30:56.280
What's going on?

30:56.280 --> 30:56.850
Dazhong,

30:57.110 --> 30:58.860
didn't you say someone broke into
your home the other day?

30:58.860 --> 31:00.350
And there were men's footprints, right?

31:00.350 --> 31:01.030
What's going on here?

31:01.030 --> 31:02.110
They might be his.

31:02.920 --> 31:04.360
What's happening?

31:04.830 --> 31:05.830
Anyway,

31:05.830 --> 31:07.160
this guy's very sneaky.

31:07.480 --> 31:08.400
I don't feel comfortable

31:08.400 --> 31:09.880
letting him stay here anymore.

31:09.880 --> 31:10.960
Don't you all agree?

31:10.960 --> 31:11.510
Right.

31:11.640 --> 31:12.380
Yeah, that's right.

31:12.380 --> 31:14.270
I never saw him here before either.

31:14.270 --> 31:15.110
Don't leave!

31:16.160 --> 31:16.750
Let go.

31:17.440 --> 31:18.640
Running away? Feeling guilty?

31:18.640 --> 31:19.680
Do you dare to show everyone

31:19.680 --> 31:20.640
what's inside this?

31:20.640 --> 31:22.370
Why should I show you anything?

31:22.950 --> 31:25.010
How dare you cause trouble in my lane!

31:26.350 --> 31:27.930
Hu Xiu, are you out of your mind?

31:27.930 --> 31:29.530
Since when is this your lane?

31:29.750 --> 31:30.920
Bullying my tenant in broad daylight—

31:30.920 --> 31:32.790
do you think I'm invisible or what?

31:32.790 --> 31:34.620
Look at the kind of tenant
you've rented to—

31:34.620 --> 31:36.650
wandering around our lane all day,

31:36.680 --> 31:37.750
looking and taking notes.

31:37.750 --> 31:38.640
Who knows, maybe he's some kind of...

31:38.640 --> 31:39.640
Some kind of what?

31:39.640 --> 31:41.440
At least he's better than someone
like you, who just loafs around all day

31:41.440 --> 31:43.200
and secretly taps into
the neighbor's electricity.

31:43.200 --> 31:44.110
You're making false accusations!

31:44.110 --> 31:45.160
False accusations?

31:45.160 --> 31:46.330
Go check the electric meter right now.

31:46.330 --> 31:47.220
You know what?

31:47.350 --> 31:49.350
Dabao did steal electricity
from neighbors before.

31:49.350 --> 31:49.680
Indeed.

31:49.680 --> 31:51.140
Don't change the subject.

31:51.200 --> 31:53.270
He wanders around the lane every day.

31:53.550 --> 31:54.480
If something happens in the future,

31:54.480 --> 31:56.210
will you take responsibility?

32:11.070 --> 32:11.830
What is this?

32:12.000 --> 32:13.200
It's just a painting.

32:13.430 --> 32:14.630
Isn't this our lane?

32:14.650 --> 32:16.510
So he's here for artistic inspiration.

32:16.510 --> 32:17.880
It's painted quite nicely.

32:17.880 --> 32:20.000
Then... What about those footprints

32:20.000 --> 32:21.130
at Dazhong's house?

32:22.070 --> 32:24.130
My friend came to see me the other day.

32:24.310 --> 32:26.110
He wasn't familiar with
the lane's environment

32:26.110 --> 32:27.750
and didn't know two households
share the same house number,

32:27.750 --> 32:29.790
so he accidentally entered your house.
I apologize.

32:29.790 --> 32:30.440
I see.

32:30.830 --> 32:32.630
It's okay. Don't worry about it.

32:34.590 --> 32:35.480
It's all cleared up.

32:35.480 --> 32:36.740
You can all go home now.

32:37.000 --> 32:38.110
Let's go.

32:38.110 --> 32:38.960
Let's go.

32:41.090 --> 32:42.420
Anything else you want?

33:12.110 --> 33:12.780
Let's talk.

33:20.540 --> 33:22.140
What brought you here today?

33:26.790 --> 33:28.530
The property management reminded me

33:28.530 --> 33:30.450
that I forgot to give my tenant,

33:30.790 --> 33:33.880
Mr. Gong Huaicong,
a copy of the lease agreement.

33:37.540 --> 33:38.260
I'm sorry.

33:38.880 --> 33:41.480
I'm the one who's actually
renting your place.

33:43.790 --> 33:44.750
I know that

33:44.920 --> 33:47.680
popular NPCs like you want to maintain

33:47.700 --> 33:48.980
an air of mystery

33:49.200 --> 33:52.060
and don't want any contact
with players in private.

33:52.070 --> 33:52.790
But

33:53.400 --> 33:55.030
since you're renting my place,

33:55.030 --> 33:56.680
you can't hide your identity from me,

33:56.680 --> 33:57.720
the landlord.

33:59.000 --> 34:00.480
Draft a new contract.

34:00.720 --> 34:02.120
I'll sign it another day.

34:03.880 --> 34:04.510
Okay.

34:19.000 --> 34:19.840
What's wrong?

34:26.070 --> 34:27.400
My interview today

34:27.670 --> 34:28.530
didn't go well.

34:29.400 --> 34:30.550
I'm a bit down.

34:31.230 --> 34:33.560
Interviewing for an architect position?

34:34.400 --> 34:35.510
How did you know?

34:36.440 --> 34:38.150
That day when I helped you
get your things prepared,

34:38.150 --> 34:39.880
I accidentally saw
your architecture portfolio

34:39.880 --> 34:40.760
and trophies.

34:44.360 --> 34:45.280
Yes.

34:45.760 --> 34:48.090
And it was a really big architecture firm.

34:48.400 --> 34:50.230
I wonder if you've heard of it.

34:50.960 --> 34:52.489
The firm's name is Zhuling.

34:55.800 --> 34:58.590
But they only wanted to hire me
as a GM assistant.

35:00.360 --> 35:02.420
They didn't even take a single look at

35:02.450 --> 35:03.980
the model I brought with me.

35:08.380 --> 35:10.040
I noticed your model just now.

35:10.840 --> 35:13.110
Being able to produce
a work like this as a student

35:13.110 --> 35:14.840
is actually quite impressive.

35:15.770 --> 35:17.630
You're just trying to comfort me.

35:18.920 --> 35:20.250
I never comfort people.

35:21.510 --> 35:22.880
As a bookstore design,

35:23.450 --> 35:25.610
it at least has some memorable features.

35:25.610 --> 35:27.570
You can tell it's a bookstore?

35:29.440 --> 35:31.150
I designed it based on

35:31.150 --> 35:32.360
the Jiangnan courtyard style.

35:32.360 --> 35:34.020
Reading books in the corridor

35:34.150 --> 35:35.780
not only creates a unique atmosphere,

35:35.780 --> 35:38.170
but also brings people closer together.

35:40.030 --> 35:41.030
That year,

35:41.800 --> 35:44.130
Galaxy Bookstore was built on Binhe Road.

35:44.670 --> 35:47.270
That designer became
an overnight sensation.

35:48.000 --> 35:49.280
I thought to myself at that time

35:49.280 --> 35:52.810
that I'd definitely design
something better than his someday.

35:52.950 --> 35:54.080
What happened then?

35:54.480 --> 35:55.840
Then...

35:57.230 --> 35:58.760
That "someday" never came.

35:59.960 --> 36:01.480
I gave up on design.

36:01.740 --> 36:06.290
♪ Close your eyes for me ♪

36:04.190 --> 36:04.960
Why?

36:07.710 --> 36:09.320
Maybe some paths, once you miss them,

36:07.810 --> 36:09.980
♪ Don't rush to wake up ♪

36:10.070 --> 36:11.840
are hard to turn back to.

36:10.460 --> 36:13.680
♪ Before the night ends ♪

36:14.230 --> 36:16.490
I thought today might be
a turning point.

36:16.560 --> 36:21.880
♪ Will you stay with me? ♪

36:22.800 --> 36:24.800
♪ I won't search for ♪

36:24.590 --> 36:25.360
So...

36:25.600 --> 36:28.410
♪ The reason we met ♪

36:26.920 --> 36:29.520
Are you planning to
accept that job at Zhuling?

36:29.630 --> 36:31.760
If I continue to work as a GM assistant,

36:30.220 --> 36:35.750
♪ The city gradually turns pale
outside the window ♪

36:33.150 --> 36:33.840
I'll really have nothing to do

36:33.840 --> 36:36.570
with architecture design
for the rest of my life.

36:37.130 --> 36:39.250
♪ The stars twinkle ♪

36:40.240 --> 36:44.250
♪ I've quieted down ♪

36:44.000 --> 36:45.060
It's getting late.

36:45.400 --> 36:46.320
I should go.

36:45.980 --> 36:49.180
♪ What kind of story will you like? ♪

36:46.880 --> 36:48.140
Thanks for the coffee.

36:48.280 --> 36:49.010
I'm off then.

36:49.300 --> 36:50.960
♪ Would you join me? ♪

36:50.990 --> 36:54.750
♪ To make a long, romantic dream ♪

36:52.360 --> 36:53.070
Oh right,

36:54.000 --> 36:55.460
I haven't asked your name.

36:55.470 --> 36:58.040
♪ Just you and me ♪

36:57.920 --> 36:59.000
Just call me Yu.

36:59.670 --> 37:00.480
Yu?

37:00.710 --> 37:01.530
Which Yu?

37:00.760 --> 37:02.940
♪ Briefly, beyond the clamor ♪

37:01.800 --> 37:02.970
The "Yu" as in "extended eaves."

37:02.970 --> 37:04.950
♪ Carefully drawing close to you ♪

37:04.980 --> 37:08.420
♪ Clinging to that trace of unknown joy ♪

37:05.030 --> 37:05.880
You know...

37:06.110 --> 37:07.460
"To the south stands the Yan Pavilion,"

37:07.460 --> 37:08.800
"its extended eaves, Yu,
hanging in gentle curves."

37:08.800 --> 37:10.000
"Walking along the veranda
to change garments,"

37:08.860 --> 37:12.550
♪ Oh, special night ♪

37:10.110 --> 37:12.800
"the circuit spans about
the distance of a short walk."

37:12.800 --> 37:14.280
That actually fits quite well with

37:14.280 --> 37:15.610
what we were just talking about.

37:15.610 --> 37:20.300
♪ I need you maybe ♪

37:17.280 --> 37:18.740
See you next time then, Yu.

37:21.590 --> 37:23.590
♪ The crowds are gone ♪

37:24.270 --> 37:27.800
♪ My thoughts have sunk to the bottom ♪

37:29.920 --> 37:35.050
♪ Maybe you never noticed me at all ♪

37:36.760 --> 37:42.300
♪ Yet you're in my view ♪

37:39.360 --> 37:40.000
Ms. Hu,

37:40.110 --> 37:41.510
have you made a decision?

37:43.910 --> 37:46.450
♪ Escape the world ♪

37:46.110 --> 37:46.800
Hello.

37:46.480 --> 37:48.480
♪ Forget all things ♪

37:47.110 --> 37:48.760
After careful consideration of
my career plans,

37:48.500 --> 37:51.860
♪ And fall down a long, romantic dream ♪

37:48.960 --> 37:51.280
I've decided to decline
your company's job offer.

37:51.280 --> 37:52.000
Thank you!

37:51.880 --> 37:54.190
♪ Just you and me ♪

37:54.880 --> 37:57.200
♪ Under moonlight ♪

37:59.560 --> 38:02.130
♪ Briefly, beyond the clamor ♪

38:02.170 --> 38:04.070
♪ Getting closer to you secretly ♪

38:04.090 --> 38:07.940
♪ Clinging to that trace of unknown joy ♪

38:08.330 --> 38:12.340
♪ Oh, special night ♪

38:15.570 --> 38:19.840
♪ We will meet tomorrow ♪

38:21.200 --> 38:22.810
♪ I know ♪

39:02.340 --> 39:04.720
[Zhuling Group]

39:05.110 --> 39:05.570
Mr. Pei,

39:05.840 --> 39:07.190
regarding the recruitment deadline
for the GM assistant position,

39:07.190 --> 39:08.840
we may need to extend it a bit.

39:09.230 --> 39:10.230
So far,

39:10.230 --> 39:12.630
we haven't found a suitable candidate yet.

39:13.190 --> 39:14.620
What about the girl
who came in yesterday afternoon?

39:14.620 --> 39:15.390
How was she?

39:15.410 --> 39:16.080
She...

39:16.590 --> 39:17.880
She was pretty good,

39:18.510 --> 39:19.360
but

39:19.630 --> 39:20.800
she declined our offer.

39:20.800 --> 39:22.400
What was her reason?

39:22.760 --> 39:24.360
She wants to be an architect.

40:08.550 --> 40:09.610
Careful, it's hot.

40:12.510 --> 40:14.770
So you're giving up on Zhuling like that?

40:16.670 --> 40:18.230
This might actually be a good thing.

40:18.230 --> 40:19.010
I did the math—

40:19.010 --> 40:20.930
from here to Zhuling,

40:20.950 --> 40:22.410
the commute alone would be exhausting.

40:22.410 --> 40:23.000
Besides,

40:23.670 --> 40:25.320
after I finished the interview last time,

40:25.320 --> 40:27.570
I couldn't even bring myself
to take a taxi.

40:27.570 --> 40:28.170
Alright.

40:28.480 --> 40:29.810
That's a good attitude.

40:37.840 --> 40:40.150
Mom, I forgot to take it with me
last time.

40:40.440 --> 40:41.920
Since I forgot,
let's just forget about it.

40:41.920 --> 40:43.180
You and Dad can keep it.

40:46.150 --> 40:47.800
It's okay, Xiu.

40:47.800 --> 40:49.400
Your dad and I will bring it to you.

40:49.400 --> 40:50.920
We're already on our way.

40:52.880 --> 40:53.670
Gong Huaicong.

40:53.670 --> 40:55.870
Gong Huaicong. Gong Huaicong. Gong...

40:56.280 --> 40:56.930
Gong...

41:04.230 --> 41:05.560
The door isn't open yet.

41:06.800 --> 41:07.880
Zhao, help me put these away.

41:07.880 --> 41:09.610
I-I need to go back for a moment.

41:16.530 --> 41:17.300
Sir,

41:17.510 --> 41:19.570
could you drive a bit faster? Thanks.

41:20.590 --> 41:21.250
Be careful.

41:25.670 --> 41:26.360
Dad! Mom!

41:29.560 --> 41:30.370
Xiu.

41:30.710 --> 41:32.840
Why did you get off work so early today?

41:33.440 --> 41:34.440
I...

41:34.460 --> 41:35.940
I was out on an errand, and...

41:35.940 --> 41:37.660
I figured it was about time to
get off work anyway, so I clocked out.

41:37.660 --> 41:38.790
What errand?

41:40.760 --> 41:42.590
I, uh, delivered a document.

41:43.270 --> 41:44.880
Look at you, all out of breath.

41:44.880 --> 41:46.000
Come on, let's get inside.

41:46.000 --> 41:46.710
-I…
-Come on.

41:46.710 --> 41:47.150
Let's go.

41:47.150 --> 41:47.960
Let's go. Come on.

41:47.960 --> 41:49.160
Let's go talk inside.

41:57.880 --> 41:58.630
I...

41:59.920 --> 42:01.050
Mom, Dad, actually,

42:01.110 --> 42:02.800
I forgot my keys today.

42:03.670 --> 42:05.110
Why didn't you say so earlier?

42:05.110 --> 42:06.440
I brought the spare key.

42:09.250 --> 42:09.850
You did?

42:10.070 --> 42:10.880
L-Let me.

42:10.880 --> 42:11.400
Let me.

42:12.110 --> 42:13.970
Which key is it? There are so many.

42:14.230 --> 42:17.030
You don't even recognize
the key to your own house?

42:17.550 --> 42:18.590
This short one.

42:22.250 --> 42:22.960
Dad! Mom!

42:22.990 --> 42:24.390
I'm opening the door now!

42:24.880 --> 42:25.550
What is this about?

42:25.550 --> 42:27.400
We haven't gone deaf, alright?

42:27.770 --> 42:28.690
I-I'm opening it!
